thread.title: CMS WebSite Services reviewed by Dave Evans
thread.title_full: CMS WebSite Services reviewed by Dave Evans

author: Dave Evans
title: CMS WebSite Services reviewed by Dave Evans
text:
We contracted with CMS WebSite Services last year to re-design our website. It took us some time to actually get the project started but once we did CMS proved to be the right company for the job. They have been nothing but professional and easy to work with and their word is beyond reproach. Our new website is very close to completion and everyone who sees it has nothing but good things to say about it. I would recommend CMS WebSite Services to anyone thinking about having any website work done...
Dave Evans
Head of Technology
The Ocean County Library
